{"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/SQ"],"kind":"relationships"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/endpoints","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/paths","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routes","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routesByPath","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/security","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/underlyingDocument"]},{"title":"Subscripts","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/subscript(dynamicMember:)"]},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/Equatable-Implementations"],"generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openapikit\/resolveddocument"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@dynamicMemberLookup"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"platforms":["Linux"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPI documents have two distinct forms of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"distributing information such that not all relevant"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"bits of information are available in one structural"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"part of an OpenAPI Document."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Documents can contain references. This is great","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"because authors can make one part of an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenAPI document more concise by referencing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a component instead of writing it inline and it also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allows shared definitions to be re-used throughout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the document.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Documents can define and override certain things at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"different levels of their structure. For example, a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"document may define a shared set of Security","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Requirements at the root and then override those","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Security Requirements for particular Operations.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both of these features of OpenAPI documents make it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"impossible to answer certain questions about a particular"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"route or endpoint without looking to multiple disparate parts"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the document and then applying certain rules to determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the relevant semantic definition of the route or endpoint being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"studied."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPIKit defines canonical forms (i.e. the only true definitions)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of endpoints, routes, and the whole document. These types (named"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedEndpoint"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedRoute"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"each allow you to get complete information about the respective components"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"without looking to other parts of the document."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You want to know what all of the parameters for a particular ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PATCH"},{"text":" endpoint are.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Without the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedEndpoint"},{"text":" type, you would need to look at the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OpenAPI.Operation"},{"text":" representing the endpoint, the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OpenAPI.PathItem"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"representing the route containing the endpoint, and you would need to potentially","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resolve references to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OpenAPI.Components"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":", the same task is much simpler:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["let document: OpenAPI.Document = ...","","let resolvedDocument = try document","    .locallyDereferenced()","    .resolved()","","let endpoint = resolvedDocument","    .routesByPath[\"\/example\/path\"]!.patch!","","\/\/ This will be all parameters defined anywhere that","\/\/ apply to this endpoint:","let parameters = endpoint.parameters"]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A resolved document is a fully dereferenced"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenAPI document that has been further distilled"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to canonical representations of each component. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":" by calling the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resolved()"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method on a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DereferencedDocument"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"metadata":{"title":"ResolvedDocument","roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"externalID":"s:10OpenAPIKit16ResolvedDocumentV","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ResolvedDocument"}],"modules":[{"name":"OpenAPIKit"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://OpenAPIKit/documentation/OpenAPIKit/ResolvedDocument/paths":{"title":"paths","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"paths"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DereferencedPathItem","preciseIdentifier":"s:10OpenAPIKit20DereferencedPathItemV"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Map","preciseIdentifier":"s:10OpenAPIKit20DereferencedPathItemV3Mapa"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/openapikit\/resolveddocument\/paths","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/paths","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This property maps the path of each route ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OpenAPI.Path"},{"type":"text","te